{"tid":1783074,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"《人命關天，麻煩推上熱門》紐約時報特派記者為上位岀賣手足","createTime":"2019-12-14T13:18:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T10:27:34.000Z","uid":176405,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"7ab4a23337fe67d5b9703439c322170687110c0c","tid":1783074,"uid":176405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T13:18:43.000Z","msg":"依位記者就係佢。<br />\nCora Engelbrecht。<br />\n首先俾佢張記者證大家睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QtRaMqf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQtRaMqf.jpg&h=4ef5f7f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢係一位Video Journalist，佢上一篇報道就係The Last Letter，前線抗爭者嘅遺書。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/g9QIETD4QV0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fg9QIETD4QV0&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWnwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=61975397\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/g9QIETD4QV0</a><br />\n<br />\n然後大家睇下依篇：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1774770/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1774770/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://today.line.me/TW/article/紐時曝百名港示威者逃亡來台！台灣教會牧師成居中協調者-KrG2zn?utm_source=fbshare\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2FTW%2Farticle%2F%E7%B4%90%E6%99%82%E6%9B%9D%E7%99%BE%E5%90%8D%E6%B8%AF%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E9%80%83%E4%BA%A1%E4%BE%86%E5%8F%B0%EF%BC%81%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%95%99%E6%9C%83%E7%89%A7%E5%B8%AB%E6%88%90%E5%B1%85%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%94%E8%AA%BF%E8%80%85-KrG2zn%3Futm_source%3Dfbshare&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWnwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=eb72b228\" target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/TW/article/紐時曝百名港示威者逃亡來台！台灣教會牧師成居中協調者-KrG2zn?utm_source=fbshare</a><br />\n<br />\n原文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.nytimes.com/2019/12/08/world/asia/hong-kong-taiwan-protests.amp.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2019%2F12%2F08%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-taiwan-protests.amp.html&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWnwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=01f54987\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.nytimes.com/2019/12/08/world/asia/hong-kong-taiwan-protests.amp.html</a><br />\n<br />\n首先，我個人警告過佢做依個題材極為敏感，唔建議佢做，當時佢話手足嘅安全係佢嘅唯一考慮。<br />\n事後證明報道大於香港人安全。<br />\n//最近有一名抗議者透露她被香港警察強姦後懷孕，希望能到台灣進行流產手術。另外，在香港理工大學圍城戰後，有10多名學生來台灣請黃春生協助取得台灣某所大學的臨時學生簽證。還有一名香港母親打電話請求替向警投擲汽油彈的14歲兒子找新的監護人//<br />\n如果對手足安全稍為重視嘅人都知道要起一個人完全唔難，加上以上嘅原話已經可以令到一個人坐10年以上。<br />\n<br />\n佢對於受訪者嘅私隱尊重係完全零<br />\n<br />\n最嚴重係條片，<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vdGkaYUg5rY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvdGkaYUg5rY&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWnwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=317a2a3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vdGkaYUg5rY</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但我身為一個抗爭者，我同大家講，絕對不能接受呢個記者的訪問，佢置受訪者於險境都要報導，唔會好好保護你。<br />\n有受訪者做完專訪同佢講，考慮過都唔想岀街，佢竟然話「Sorry I can&rsquo;t do that.」受害人話係咪即使佢有生命危險都唔會撤回，佢都話係。<br />\n<br />\n又同中間人承諾唔會影樣，第一次見面唔會做任何interview / record，佢見到受訪者就俾壓力對方話自己專誠美國過嚟，一定要交野又話可以保護對方，最後就偷影、咩都岀。問題瘋狂引導式問題，etc。層岀不窮。<br />\n<br />\n最後同大家講，<br />\n接受訪問，唔該諗清楚咩可以講咩唔可以講，你冇危險，但你身邊嘅人會因為你所作所為付出生命代價。<br />\n<br />\n我知好多人以為好小事，但真係會有手足因為佢依篇報道被消失，亦都有手足已經因為佢以家已經陷入絕境。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">手足唔該推上熱門，我地怕再有手足中伏。</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"a68f896c3b4a6091022366dae547fa8f5d3bb261","tid":1783074,"uid":251769,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T13:19:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請各位喺出post前貼多張日程表or文宣</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁文宣組就冇咁忙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zrNpRn5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzrNpRn5.jpg&h=7453738e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Hhk89N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Hhk89N.jpg&h=e421777a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FPC5APO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFPC5APO.jpg&h=08184019&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d999bf1bfbd7e54349971ddd966701e4fbd1dfe9","tid":1783074,"uid":176405,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T13:20:58.000Z","msg":"希望各位手足可以認真看待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推上熱門"},{"pid":"60130d188bbccc84feebe3aafb1e9ed4c723f210","tid":1783074,"uid":283906,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T13:21:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"631932812e645f5abe8781afa7ea7960425aa42c","tid":1783074,"uid":39174,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T13:21:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a3b0cce6bdc6dbb23a85911fe5f715651859537","tid":1783074,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T13:22:20.000Z","msg":"冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5ecaabce04ea64f62f3483f2fd08314571b8eeae","tid":1783074,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T13:22:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> you fucking white trash"},{"pid":"facb7d71fbf7cb66ecb9ae9b690ce466dbfd3719","tid":1783074,"uid":176405,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T13:23:22.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">我唔想再有手足被消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"